Envelope¶

The envelope of the incident laser field varies according to $$ P(t)= \begin{cases} & exp\left({\frac{-(t-T/2)^p}{(0.15*T)^p}}\right) \text{ for } 0 \leq t \le T \\ & 0 \; \text{ otherwise } \end{cases} $$ $$p=4$$

In [ ]:
t_max = las_time
samples = 1000
In [ ]:
def supr_gaus_env(t,p):
    if t<las_time:
        n=(t-0.5*las_time)**p
        d = (0.15*las_time)**p
        a  = np.sin(2*np.pi*t/tau)
        
        return a*np.exp(-(n/d))
    else:
        return 0
